Task 1:
-------

Find the username.

Task 2:
-------

List the users who are currently logged in.

Task 3:
-------

Find out the current operating system you are working on.

Task 4:
-------

Find the release number of the distribution of the operating system.

Task 5:
-------

Find the amount of disk space available on the file system.

Task 6:
-------

Find the amount of physical and swap memory used by the system.

Task 7:
-------

Print a calendar of the current month.

